channel.title: **SOLD** For sale: 1 Axoloti Core
channel.description:
Hi guys,
A while ago I finally pulled the trigger on buying an Axoloti Core and I was eagerly waiting to buy an enclosure, but the one I wanted had been out of stock for a long time and they don't return my messages. Long story short: I kind of lost interest, but I also won't have any time soon to start with this project. Both reasons made me realize that I'd better sell my Axoloti Core. I'm located in Antwerp, Belgium. Local pickup or sent by mail (BE/EU) are possible.
Hit me up with a message!
Thanks!
